### Gallery API - Testing Endpoints

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3004
@providerId = 1
@serviceId = 5

### 1. Upload Single Image
POST {{baseUrl}}/gallery/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="providerId"

{{providerId}}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="serviceId"

{{serviceId}}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="imageTitle"

Trabajo terminado - Ejemplo
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="imageDescription"

Descripción del trabajo realizado
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="displayOrder"

0
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="test-image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 2. Get all images for a service
GET {{baseUrl}}/gallery/service/{{serviceId}}

### 3. Get single image by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/gallery/1

### 4. Create gallery entry with URL
POST {{baseUrl}}/gallery
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serviceId": {{serviceId}},
  "providerId": {{providerId}},
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
  "imageTitle": "Título de ejemplo",
  "imageDescription": "Descripción de ejemplo",
  "displayOrder": 0
}

### 5. Delete image
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/gallery/1

### 6. Toggle approval
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/gallery/1/approve

### 7. Get provider images (if you add this endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/gallery/provider/{{providerId}}
